    "en": {
      "title": "Russia to supply missile systems to Belarus",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Russia will supply Belarus with Iskander-M missile systems, Russian President Vladimir Putin has said during talks with Belarusian President Alexander Lukashenko.",
        "He added that the distribution will take place within a few months.",
        "The Iskander-M is a mobile guided missile system with a range of up to 500 km (300 miles). Missiles can carry conventional or nuclear warheads."
      ],
